title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Dec 16 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Dec 16 2021
description:
C&B agree: Everyone knows Biden’s first year is a disaster. Kamala Harris says she and Biden haven’t discussed running for re-election in 2024. San Francisco car break-ins are so high it's prompting some car owners to leave their trunks open. Clay and Buck welcome Kat Timpf, host of FOX Nation’s Sincerely, Kat to discuss the UPenn swimmer, Biden/Kamala 2024 and liberals celebrating the burning of Fox's Christmas tree. Fauciites lay the groundwork to limit capacity to the Super Bowl. We are now at 700 days of "fifteen days to stop the spread." Will China and Russia be emboldened to invade Taiwan and Ukraine because of the weak Biden administration?
